T1  - Factor based index tracking
AU  - Corielli, Francesco
AU  - Marcellino, Massimiliano
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 30
IS  - 8
SP  - 2215
EP  - 2233
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/08/01/
